                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#26v" facs="030"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1077ArchangelMichael"/> and the three youths in the fiery furnace</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#34v" facs="038"/><desc>A poor man holding a knife and fish. Corresponds to the miracle on the facing page</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#40v" facs="044"/><desc><persName ref="PRS8469Samson"/> killed the Philistines by the jawbone of a donkey. This is a modern interpretation with Samson and the Philistines also carrying rifles.</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#58v" facs="062"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1077ArchangelMichael"/> and Bäläʿam the magician</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#67v" facs="071"/><desc>An image of a miracle of the archangel Michael. A woman sleeps under a tree next to a mesob. A man with a sword stands over her</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#72r" facs="075"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1077ArchangelMichael"/> rescuing <persName ref="PRS3337Daniel"/> in the lionsʾ den</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#86v" facs="090"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1077ArchangelMichael"/> spears a demon while ʾÄfomya stands nearby</desc></decoNote>
